# -------------------------------------------------
# Test-time codegen (cOde / CppODE write per-test C/C++ files
# into tests/testthat/; they're ephemeral and must not be tracked).
# bloq_*.cpp, obsfn.cpp and expl_parfn_*.cpp are tracked fixtures,
# so the ignore patterns below stay narrow on purpose.
# -------------------------------------------------
tests/testthat/*.c
tests/testthat/odemodel*.cpp
tests/testthat/decay_des_*
tests/testthat/petab_fixture_*
tests/testthat/rep_trafo_*
tests/testthat/focei_*
tests/testthat/bloq_p_*.c
tests/testthat/reactions_for_Alyssa_model.csv
# tracked-fixture allowlist (in case * patterns above ever broaden)
!tests/testthat/bloq_err.cpp
!tests/testthat/bloq_obs.cpp
!tests/testthat/bloq_p_C1.cpp
!tests/testthat/bloq_p_err_C1.cpp
!tests/testthat/expl_parfn_C1.cpp
!tests/testthat/expl_parfn_steady.cpp
!tests/testthat/obsfn.cpp

# -------------------------------------------------
# Python caches (inst/code helpers shelled out via reticulate)
# -------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# -------------------------------------------------
# Claude stuff
# -------------------------------------------------
CLAUDE.md
/doc/
/Meta/
